reviews_data.review_text: Perfect little coffee shop. Great espresso drinks, well lit from the big windows, and comfy seating. Was surprised it wasn’t as busy given how great it is. A hidden gem for now, but I expect that won’t last.
Sara was really nice.  Very comfortable environment and my mocha was great!!
great coffee! great taste!
Great location, adorable coffee shop and it’s night swim coffee which is *the best*. Sarah is fantastic!!
A lovely day starts here. One of the best vibes of any coffee shop in CLT, with massive high ceiling windows that fill the space with light and energy!
Wonderful coffee shop, Sarah was so nice! The environment is so pleasant, I especially liked the loft.
Comfortable and clean place 😍

Btw whoever was on aux was playing some bangers lol
Solid coffee shop with enough space to get work done. They have a second floor too which helps if the main area gets busy. I had the flat white and it was phenomenal smooth, strong, and just the right amount of milk. Will definitely be back.
Great seconds location! Tons of seating and super bright and nice environment. Pretty empty compared to the first location down the street, so great place to work.
Great coffee, nice ambience!

Friendly and welcoming atmosphere! Sarah was so kind! Great coffee with natural sweetener options! They sell coffee beans and a few baked goods, there’s also a loft area for more privacy. Will definitely be visiting more often!
It was my first time here, and I found  both the coffee and atmosphere to be great
Cute coffeeshop :)
A great coffee spot! Noah is the best there!!
Beautiful place best coffee
